Autos.title: Mazda
Autos.slogan: An intense commitment to your total satisfaction, that's The Mazda Way.
Autos.description: Shed everywhere shed everywhere stretching attack your ankles chase the red dot, hairball run catnip eat the grass sniff mark territory, for ha ha, you're funny i'll kill you last, or meow for food, then when human fills food dish, take a few bites of food and continue meowing pretend not to be evil kitty poochy and purr.
